- Confidence 0.8+ = satisfied, 0.5-0.79 = partial, <0.5 = not satisfied
- `overall_passes` = true only if ALL critical requirements have confidence >= 0.8
- `needs_rewrite` = true if any critical requirement has confidence < 0.5
